# REST Client (VS Code / Cursor extension: "REST Client" by Huachao Mao)
#
# 1. Put LEADERBOARD_SNAPSHOT_CRON_SECRET in repo-root `.env` (gitignored), OR
# 2. Replace {{cronSecret}} below with a literal (never commit real secrets).
#
# Click "Send Request" above each ### block.

@baseUrl = https://rosterriddles.com
@cronSecret = {{$dotenv LEADERBOARD_SNAPSHOT_CRON_SECRET}}

### Rebuild leaderboard snapshots — Bearer (preferred)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/v1/leaderboard-snapshots/rebuild
Authorization: Bearer {{cronSecret}}

### Rebuild leaderboard snapshots — X-Cron-Secret (same auth as Bearer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/v1/leaderboard-snapshots/rebuild
X-Cron-Secret: {{cronSecret}}
